===Verb===
'''짚다''' (''jipda'')
#To [[rely]], [[rest]] (''on a [[cane]], [[stick]], etc.'')
#* 땅 짚고 헤엄치기 (''ttang jipgo heeom-chigi'') As easy or safe as swimming (with the arms) resting on the ground.
#To [[dip]] (''a [[dipstick]] to stand on the bottom'')
#To [[point]] (''at something spefific as (if) with a finger'')   
#To [[touch]], [[feel]] (''at some body part to [[examine]] the temperature, pulses, etc.'')
#To [[guess]], [[estimate]] (''relying on, or starting from, some baseline'') 

